    "description": "World League Baseball is a baseball game that anyone can pick up and play easily.<br>Rendered in a brand-new casual art style, it also has a character growth system with a high degree of freedom.<br><br>[Features]<br>● A full-on baseball experience with simple and easy controls!<br>&quot;World League Baseball&quot; is a baseball game with very easy-to-learn controls that lets anyone throw a fastball or hit a home run with ease.<br><br>● Build up a &quot;World League&quot; team to win the league!<br>Excel in each division to receive a huge sum of prize money. Recruit skilled players and continue to build up your team to ultimately become league champions!<br><br>● Play against players from around the world in a real-time &quot;Online Match&quot;!<br>The &quot;Online Match&quot; is a multiplayer mode that is season-based. Play games in real time and win to earn Game Points and raise your tier. The higher the tier, the greater the reward!<br><br>● Train a specific player through a &quot;Private Lesson&quot;.<br>Choose a player to train from one of your nine key players. Control the chosen player directly and get stellar results for a chance to acquire more EXP and rewards.<br><br>● A character growth system with a high degree of freedom.<br>Collect player EXP and cards to raise a player's level and acquire various skills by leveling up. Each player's skill could be customized to match your strategy and style.<br><br>● Brand-new concepts to enjoy.<br>Play ball with over 300 unique players from 12 teams in stadiums built with unique concepts in mind, such as a giant stone statue, a temple, a dragon, and more.",
